  "content": "<p data-pid=\"aAzWAgQr\">再说艾宾浩斯发明记忆法的，我见一个锤一个：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5d834eac50ad56cc695c609074b8c7c5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"684\" data-rawheight=\"874\" data-original-token=\"v2-5d834eac50ad56cc695c609074b8c7c5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-56403c117801428704fa9a64a2e0d0ef_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"684\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-5d834eac50ad56cc695c609074b8c7c5_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;684&#39; height=&#39;874&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"684\" data-rawheight=\"874\" data-original-token=\"v2-5d834eac50ad56cc695c609074b8c7c5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-56403c117801428704fa9a64a2e0d0ef_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"684\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-5d834eac50ad56cc695c609074b8c7c5_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5d834eac50ad56cc695c609074b8c7c5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"_P8CiRs3\">这位答主提到了一本书，叫做《记忆力心理学》，我琢磨着艾宾浩斯写过这本书吗？于是搜了一下，发现豆瓣里还真有：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a6ec21c373718cc52c173a7777a70cd9_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"704\" data-rawheight=\"278\" data-original-token=\"v2-a6ec21c373718cc52c173a7777a70cd9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-4b6a4052063073b5a8e6fa996fad6821_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"704\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a6ec21c373718cc52c173a7777a70cd9_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;704&#39; height=&#39;278&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"704\" data-rawheight=\"278\" data-original-token=\"v2-a6ec21c373718cc52c173a7777a70cd9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-4b6a4052063073b5a8e6fa996fad6821_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"704\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a6ec21c373718cc52c173a7777a70cd9_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a6ec21c373718cc52c173a7777a70cd9_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"juinNT7X\">于是我就把这本书找来看看。通过对比原版，我发现了一个令人震惊的事实：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cb11e27a4f7508e245e8010f2425bdac_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"480\" data-rawheight=\"748\" data-original-token=\"v2-cb11e27a4f7508e245e8010f2425bdac\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-953d7812ee9f68c93f2c95aa5c70a02b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"480\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-cb11e27a4f7508e245e8010f2425bdac_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;480&#39; height=&#39;748&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"480\" data-rawheight=\"748\" data-original-token=\"v2-cb11e27a4f7508e245e8010f2425bdac\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-953d7812ee9f68c93f2c95aa5c70a02b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"480\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-cb11e27a4f7508e245e8010f2425bdac_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cb11e27a4f7508e245e8010f2425bdac_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"BDsaeGSp\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//archive.org/details/memorycontributi00ebbiuoft/page/vi/mode/2up\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Memory; a contribution to experimental psychology : Ebbinghaus, Hermann, 1850-1909 : Free Download, Borrow, and Streaming : Internet Archive</a></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1331de0d9d7ac9ec9c06d3b6c413c8a9_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-original-token=\"v2-1331de0d9d7ac9ec9c06d3b6c413c8a9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-96a6a6011baac2dd6bce29b357c7de1f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-1331de0d9d7ac9ec9c06d3b6c413c8a9_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;960&#39; height=&#39;1080&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"1080\" data-original-token=\"v2-1331de0d9d7ac9ec9c06d3b6c413c8a9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-96a6a6011baac2dd6bce29b357c7de1f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-1331de0d9d7ac9ec9c06d3b6c413c8a9_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1331de0d9d7ac9ec9c06d3b6c413c8a9_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"7cWTHZhH\">这营销号的味也太冲了吧？艾宾浩斯原文完全不是这种语调。不仅如此，</p><h2>这两本书，连目录都对不上！</h2><p data-pid=\"ifsX-4Wf\">《记忆力心理学》的介绍里甚至没有提原版书的名字，这已经让我很奇怪了。没想到内容更是私货满满。自己瞎编了一个复习方法，然后冠上艾宾浩斯之名。</p><p data-pid=\"cgw1PmCE\">当然，可能会有读者朋友问，会不会你找错原版书了？其实翻译的是另外一本？</p><p data-pid=\"iZadjZ8k\">那我建议看看下面两张内容对比：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-29e0ba21f144e3057c4ee65ce8717a93_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"963\" data-rawheight=\"754\" data-original-token=\"v2-29e0ba21f144e3057c4ee65ce8717a93\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6401140cc2f2e27ede6c78e6d433e48b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"963\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-29e0ba21f144e3057c4ee65ce8717a93_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;963&#39; height=&#39;754&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"963\" data-rawheight=\"754\" data-original-token=\"v2-29e0ba21f144e3057c4ee65ce8717a93\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6401140cc2f2e27ede6c78e6d433e48b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"963\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-29e0ba21f144e3057c4ee65ce8717a93_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-29e0ba21f144e3057c4ee65ce8717a93_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c35e69fd111e4bb4752548806d61e8f8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1641\" data-rawheight=\"1053\" data-original-token=\"v2-c35e69fd111e4bb4752548806d61e8f8\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-110da8a4340eddd9f6e5a561da266b7a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1641\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c35e69fd111e4bb4752548806d61e8f8_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1641&#39; height=&#39;1053&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1641\" data-rawheight=\"1053\" data-original-token=\"v2-c35e69fd111e4bb4752548806d61e8f8\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-110da8a4340eddd9f6e5a561da266b7a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1641\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c35e69fd111e4bb4752548806d61e8f8_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c35e69fd111e4bb4752548806d61e8f8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"QEogdR7z\">讨论科学实验的时候，总算是不敢夹带私货，改为直译原文了是吧。我真的服。</p><h2>艾宾浩斯发明记忆法了吗？</h2><p data-pid=\"hmNnIyDV\">答案是，没有！所谓网上流传的 5 分钟、30 分钟、12 小时、1 天、2 天、4 天、7 天、15 天是怎么来的？我找到了出处：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8a5125f13da01084d5e50a0caa0bd858_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"479\" data-rawheight=\"747\" data-original-token=\"v2-8a5125f13da01084d5e50a0caa0bd858\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-426c623ed13c4187660026d8d5c2eb3a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"479\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8a5125f13da01084d5e50a0caa0bd858_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;479&#39; height=&#39;747&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"479\" data-rawheight=\"747\" data-original-token=\"v2-8a5125f13da01084d5e50a0caa0bd858\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-426c623ed13c4187660026d8d5c2eb3a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"479\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8a5125f13da01084d5e50a0caa0bd858_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8a5125f13da01084d5e50a0caa0bd858_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"WoRsGCBv\">虽然数字上接近，但含义却完全不同——艾宾浩斯实际上做了 163 组双重测试（首次记忆+再次记忆），这些实验被分为 7 组，再次记忆与首次记忆之间分别相隔 0.33 小时、1 小时、8.8 小时、24 小时、24 小时、6 天、31 天。所以这些复习间隔并不是连续的！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d1ab524bcede8cb51de54a66d31d0c20_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"993\" data-rawheight=\"807\" data-original-token=\"v2-d1ab524bcede8cb51de54a66d31d0c20\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-b200ef6b2f00d3fc8490c5d38c099c59_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"993\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-d1ab524bcede8cb51de54a66d31d0c20_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;993&#39; height=&#39;807&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"993\" data-rawheight=\"807\" data-original-token=\"v2-d1ab524bcede8cb51de54a66d31d0c20\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-b200ef6b2f00d3fc8490c5d38c099c59_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"993\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-d1ab524bcede8cb51de54a66d31d0c20_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d1ab524bcede8cb51de54a66d31d0c20_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"2ISBDrla\">其实想想也就能明白，艾宾浩斯是通过这一组实验绘制的遗忘曲线，应当保证每个时间间隔后再次记忆不受干扰。如果艾宾浩斯是连续按照这个复习周期记忆，那他的遗忘曲线应该长成下面这个样子：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-74d89f4346f1f440a351eb5f7bc99f36_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"681\" data-rawheight=\"337\" data-original-token=\"v2-74d89f4346f1f440a351eb5f7bc99f36\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-88f54781699fe51b1499a2fc8c6587d5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"681\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-74d89f4346f1f440a351eb5f7bc99f36_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;681&#39; height=&#39;337&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"681\" data-rawheight=\"337\" data-original-token=\"v2-74d89f4346f1f440a351eb5f7bc99f36\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-88f54781699fe51b1499a2fc8c6587d5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"681\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-74d89f4346f1f440a351eb5f7bc99f36_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-74d89f4346f1f440a351eb5f7bc99f36_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Yke6NKYu\">而不是这个样子：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-133452dd110c4edfe855d3ddeed2f701_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"495\" data-rawheight=\"475\" data-original-token=\"v2-133452dd110c4edfe855d3ddeed2f701\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-805f4c93100bbd8a0e7bacf7b4ffba63_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"495\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-133452dd110c4edfe855d3ddeed2f701_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;495&#39; height=&#39;475&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"495\" data-rawheight=\"475\" data-original-token=\"v2-133452dd110c4edfe855d3ddeed2f701\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-805f4c93100bbd8a0e7bacf7b4ffba63_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"495\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-133452dd110c4edfe855d3ddeed2f701_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-133452dd110c4edfe855d3ddeed2f701_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"8q_e26zB\">我实在不明白为什么总有一群人在网络上传播谣言，而且还有很多人真就信了。</p><h2>那么到底该怎么记忆？</h2><p data-pid=\"VNdPkYSd\">其实按照一个复习周期反复复习的方法，叫做间隔重复，其利用了测试效应和间隔效应来增强记忆：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/420309917\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2dbc2730b68fac71f549caab01eca920_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"2076\" data-image-height=\"1170\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：(2/5) 高效学习的间隔重复——文献综述之测试效应</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/420924493\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c411e5e812bd614048b34e5a1f48eb9f_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"2240\" data-image-height=\"1264\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：(3/5) 高效学习的间隔重复——文献综述之间隔效应</a><p data-pid=\"hDkgNh05\">关于这个方法的应用，我推荐以下两篇文章：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/65131722\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/equation.jpg\" data-image-width=\"120\" data-image-height=\"120\" class=\"internal\">mmjang：【三万字长文】量子物理学家是如何使用 Anki 的？</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/434074509\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3fc5e91c7a88c26207775c8301afbe1f_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1579\" data-image-height=\"328\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：如何写出好卡片：利用间隔重复创造理解</a><p data-pid=\"AITqrZhj\">我就帮到这里了，剩下的就靠缘分了，对间隔重复感兴趣的朋友，我相信你们在中文互联网搜索相关资料，最后都会搜索到我的，2333</p><hr/><p data-pid=\"6W_SVU0S\">防杠补丁：补充一个德语原版</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-607688a6145e7063e80019e17bb1e023_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1014\" data-rawheight=\"793\" data-original-token=\"v2-607688a6145e7063e80019e17bb1e023\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c9f2484c6d775014e66e02224cb0595e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1014\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-607688a6145e7063e80019e17bb1e023_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1014&#39; height=&#39;793&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1014\" data-rawheight=\"793\" data-original-token=\"v2-607688a6145e7063e80019e17bb1e023\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c9f2484c6d775014e66e02224cb0595e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1014\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-607688a6145e7063e80019e17bb1e023_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-607688a6145e7063e80019e17bb1e023_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"OdO6i0gZ\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.deutschestextarchiv.de/book/view/ebbinghaus_gedaechtnis_1885%3Fp%3D119\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Deutsches Textarchiv – Ebbinghaus, Hermann: Über das Gedächtnis. Leipzig, 1885.</a></p><p data-pid=\"kBMCv-vM\">补充：评论区有朋友说时间间隔不重要，反复复习才重要……我的研究表明时间间隔很重要：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.maimemo.com/paper/\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">A Stochastic Shortest Path Algorithm for Optimizing Spaced Repetition Scheduling</a><p data-pid=\"nNmuk4da\"><br/>本文已加入：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/collection/925510885\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">艾宾浩斯记忆法打假合集</a><p></p>",
